com.twitter.heron.metricsmgr.sink.tmaster

Class TMasterClient

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.twitter.heron.common.network.HeronClient
      • com.twitter.heron.metricsmgr.sink.tmaster.TMasterClient
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ISelectHandler, java.lang.Runnable

    public class TMasterClient
extends HeronClient
implements java.lang.Runnable
    TMasterClient connects to TMaster and then send TopologyMaster.PublishMetrics continuously. Note that TMaster will not send registerRequest or wait for registerResponse.
